//     d_gi = vech((x_gi − m̄_g)(x_gi − m̄_g)ᵀ) ,  s_g = vech(S_g) ,
//
// (n divisor — matches magmaan's `empirical_gamma`, the lavaan ML convention).
// The formula for S admits a casewise reduction that *never forms Γ̂*:
//
